## WABT wasm2c runtime (wasm-rt)

The non-Windows addons compile C generated by WABT's `wasm2c` tool from the
first-party PAC guest module together with WABT's wasm2c runtime sources.
Windows addons use WinHTTP and do not include this backend. The runtime is
